Follow With Care 

"Work hard, play hard" is advice 

Best taken with some caution, 

For it can bring fitness and success 

Or a state of total exhaustion. 

-- Edward F. Dempsey. 

Double Check 

The guest paid his bill at the resort hotel, and as he departed he noticed a sign saying, "Have You Left Anything?" The man went back and spoke to the desk clerk: "That sign is wrong," he said. "It should read, "Have You Anything Left?" 

-- Sam Ewing. 

